headline: The Cigna Group Health Equity Impact Fund Opens 2025 Grants
summary: The Cigna Group Foundation today announced the second year of grants from its Health Equity Impact Fund. The initiative will allocate a total of $3 million to two cities: Hartford, Conn., where it began last year, and St. Louis, Mo., which struggles with significant health disparities among its adult residents.
